               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was coming out of Black Horse-court from my brother's, and the handkerchief was <hi rend="italic">chucked</hi> down at my feet; I picked it up; there was a man standing by, who saw me pick it up; I said to him, "Did I pick this up, or did I not?" and he said, "The boy picked it up."</p>
